<P>
   ISRAEL-ELECTIONS _ JERUSALEM _ The Israeli campaigns for prime
minister drew to a close Sunday with the drama of a last-minute
withdrawal of a popular general who through his support to leftist
candidate Ehud Barak. If the polls hold up, the three-year reign of
controversial Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu could be drawing to
a close. (Kaplow, Cox News Service)
</P>
