   ISRAEL-VOTE (Jerusalem) _ In a stunning turn of events, two
minor party candidates withdrew from the prime minister's race on
Sunday, paving the way for what polls predicted what be a
conclusive victory on Monday by Labor Party leader Ehud Barak. By
Deborah Sontag.
</P>
