<HEADER>
A9375 &Cx1f; kan-z
r v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BC-KAN-BUDGET-KAN &LR;      05-16 0238
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BC-KAN-BUDGET-KAN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
   
<TEXT>
<P>
