<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-16 23:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9487 &Cx1f; tth-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MERCATA-ONLINE-SPI &LR;      05-16 1026
